inclusion.criterion: Patient is stable and in adequate clinical condition to undergo CTA + CTP
inclusion.label: met

exclusion.criterion: abnormalities, atrial fibrillation, renal insufficiency with glomerular filtration rate (GFR)
exclusion.label: not_met

notes: Patient presents with chest pain in the ED, but no ECG-signs of acute ischemia and Hs Troponine T level/evolution indicative of ischemia.
